Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never leave you again.\NYou belong only to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.78,0:00:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.56,0:00:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan... I love you.\n I love you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:44.52,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(544,330)}Volume 5
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:44.52,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(319,413)}Red Encounter
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.69,0:01:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.84,0:01:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel good. Your hand is so... warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.63,0:01:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body is also warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Onii-ch{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling a bit weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.78,0:02:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki, you're already very...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.92,0:02:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.67,0:02:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea itself, of you and me having...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly girl. Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.58,0:02:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you happy, Miyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.52,0:02:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Very.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come in, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.97,0:02:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.26,0:02:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You must eat. Otherwise, you won't make it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.13,0:03:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The last one must be in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru-sama, I detect an evil energy in that temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.99,0:03:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Amaterasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Don't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Genbu and Byakko have been freed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We only have to free Suzaku here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you can return to Ashihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take care of this quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But if Suzaku can't be freed,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,then everything will have been in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean, Amaterasu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It means...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Amaterasu! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You will die painlessly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,just like that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami. That was her name, from what I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You will see her again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}What did you do to Nanami-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... Hikaru-chan's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Touka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hold me close to her wound!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If her spirit leaves her body completely, it will be too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a miracle! Nanami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You were attacked by an evil spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru-san's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's happened to you, Amaterasu?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're completely different.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do anything against this girl, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Tsukuyomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I belong to Yomotsu Okami-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The ruler of dead souls!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.46,0:07:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the two of you together don't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How in God's name...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Amaterasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Two of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I was careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who looks like me took control of my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So that was why...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of powerful soul is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,was expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Be gone, evil spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a very nice thing to say about your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:09:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'm an evil spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's because you've made me one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking nonsense. I don't have a sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know, Amaterasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Every member of our family has the power to control dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll meet again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations! You've succeeded in freeing them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're the last one, Suzaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's not a very nice thing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to say about your sister.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miyuki,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Grandfather...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will return to you soon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.82,0:10:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Hikaru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,first met you on the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,just for this one time, to have...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,a memory that will stay with me forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hikaru-san, please don't ever forget me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A strong will can make things come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Such is the power that weaves dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Your home...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who's important to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Grandfather...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miyuki...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You stupid people!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The King of Kings, Sanou, has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Susanoo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Amaterasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this... a real sword?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, save...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,your mother, Izanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And your inheritance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Go with your four servants.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They're from Nenoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have any family and were raised here in Ashiharanoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Destiny has brought them to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki is also one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:16:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not your little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I have waited for this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No one knew when this day would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather, then I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Yomotsuhirasakai,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm relying on you, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted the tears of Ikkikun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've longed for the love of a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I envied you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I only wanted to play... with my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, we'll always be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Susanoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:18:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Brave of you to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you attacking those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all because of Yomotsu Okami,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and a wish from my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't like it, then come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Child of Izanami, born in Nenokuni and raised in Ashiharanokuni!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Child of Izanami?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Die at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanou-kun, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:18:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you brothers want to kill each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Susanoo is your little brother, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It was he who saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru-chan's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanou is your...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.28,0:19:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yomotsu Okami...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and your mother Izanami...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,were originally one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yomotsu Okami-sama was born out of Izanami's evil spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They are opposites of one another:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,a god of destruction and a god of protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then our enemy, the King of evil spirits Yomotsu Okami is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,For a long time, you people have been chasing{was: selling}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,my mother Yomotsu Okami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In reality, she is part of your treasured Izanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the child of Yomotsu Okami, Sanou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I protected my mother and killed all enemies
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,who opposed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. He's not heavily injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've learned the true reason why he was following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, to Yomotsuhirasakai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This place belongs to Yomotsu Okami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Izanami-sama's power to create dreams has built this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be at peace, Yomotsu Okami!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.19,0:21:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.44,0:21:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.90,0:21:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, everyone, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.80,0:22:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just apoligized to Nanami-chan about the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.10,0:22:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But aren't you mad about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.72,0:22:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Miyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.60,0:22:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.47,0:22:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.73,0:23:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling good?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.74,0:23:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, great, Miyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.28,0:23:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.70,0:23:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.71,0:24:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Did I hurt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.21,0:24:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.25,0:24:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a little, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.97,0:24:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy that I'm now connected with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.39,0:24:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.94,0:24:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.40,0:24:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.61,0:24:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start, but gently.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.06,0:25:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.82,0:25:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.19,0:25:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you endure it for a bit more?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.38,0:25:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,YES! YES!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.55,0:25:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.18,0:25:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.97,0:25:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.06,0:25:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.19,0:25:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.99,0:26:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Not of human origins, prodigy born out of my dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.33,0:26:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave all my love to Izanagi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.96,0:26:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the result of that love.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.21,0:26:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, I thank you!
