Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.07,0:26:37.86,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there is a phantom{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.86,0:26:44.24,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that is calling to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.47,0:27:04.31,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through the mirror, I can see the other side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.31,0:27:08.39,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The maze has started to distort space-time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.39,0:27:11.35,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You stand in front of me,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.35,0:27:15.15,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but are you real or unreal?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.36,0:27:20.82,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My legs tremble, and I fall deeply. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.11,0:27:24.37,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That proves to me {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.37,0:27:28.12,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it's a fake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.50,0:27:36.25,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Despite the many bitter memories that have hurt us,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.25,0:27:42.26,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\i1}we must fight on and achieve something.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.30,0:27:45.97,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be brave, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.97,0:27:49.39,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\i1}don't let go of my hand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.39,0:27:56.57,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's cross the bridge of hope together, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.57,0:28:00.53,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\i1}which I previously...{\i0}
